<br>
I know, first off I need to get new weapons.  I'm working on my faction right now as I have a Frostbringer head to quest.  After that I'm going to take a group to Chef/Bar/Armsman a couple times in hope of a RBG, if that doesn't work...my guild can do Tale/Sever/Trak now, so a CoF or CoP might be forseeable.  A new range slot will fall in place whenever I have the 3k to spend, sometime within the next few weeks.<br>
<br>
After that I'm lost.  I'd like a Fleshgrinder for my main hand but I know that's a bit far off, can anyone suggest something smaller to shoot for?  A guildmember's needing his 8th shawl final fight done, maybe a Snowchipper or the Hammer?<br>
<br>
Any particular order I should go in when upgrading the armor?  I can get Fierce Heraldic Armor and Earring of the Solstice pieces made for materials, so in what order should I replace them?<br>
<br>
This post was probably hard to follow, but thanks in advance for any help you can offer.<br>
